name: First Story
description:
Here is a journey with the self, so go deep into the details and receive what touches your soul.

[ In the journey of the spirit we always dive until we search and discover ourselves, we find that the light is the evidence and everything is based on love, as we up the ladder of the road we find that the truth is a part of us and we must search for, We dive into our beliefs, the seas of knowledge explode then the vision becomes clear ]
